/members. For example, the following file structure defines two explicit slots: @analytics and @team. The folder structure above means that the component in app/layout.js now accepts the @analytics and @team slots props, and
can render them in parallel alongside the children prop:
app/layout.tsx (tsx)export default function Layout(props: {
  children: React.ReactNode
  analytics: React.ReactNode
  team: React.ReactNode
}) {
  return (
    <>
      {props.children}
      {props.team}
      {props.analytics}
