VersionChanges
v14.0.0next export has been removed in favor of "output": "export"
v13.4.0App Router (Stable) adds enhanced static export support, including using React Server Components and Route Handlers. v13.3.0next export is deprecated and replaced with "output": "export"","textTemplate":"","metadataSeparator":"
