Pages in the app directory are Server Components by default. This is different from the pages directory where pages are Client
Components. Data fetching has changed in app. getServerSideProps, getStaticProps and getInitialProps have been replaced with a
simpler API. The app directory uses nested folders to define routes and a special page.js file to make a route segment publicly accessible. pagespages Directoryappapp DirectoryRoute","textTemplate":"","metadataSeparator":"
