for a given animated image, use the unoptimized prop. Responsive Images
The default generated srcset contains 1x and 2x images in order to support different device pixel ratios. However, you may wish to
render a responsive image that stretches with the viewport. In that case, youll need to set sizes as well as style (or className).","textTemplate":"","metadataSeparator":"
