errorerror
An instance of an Error object forwarded to the error.js Client Component. error.messageerror.message
The error message. For errors forwarded from Client Components, this will be the original Errors message. For errors forwarded from Server Components, this will be a generic error message to avoid leaking sensitive details.errors.digest
