To access search params in Pages (Server Components), use the searchParams prop. Layouts
Unlike Pages, Layouts (Server Components) do not receive the searchParams prop. This is because a shared layout is not re-rendered
during navigation which could lead to stale searchParams between navigations. View detailed explanation. Instead, use the Page searchParams prop or the useSearchParams hook in a Client Component, which is re-rendered on the client
