Description: Configure how data fetches are logged to the console when running Next.js in development mode. {/ The content of this doc is shared between the app and pages router. You can use the <PagesOnly>Content</PagesOnly> component
to add content that is specific to the Pages Router. Any shared content should not be wrapped in a component. /}
