Description: Configure Server Actions behavior in your Next.js application. Options for configuring Server Actions behavior in your Next.js application.allowedOriginsallowedOrigins
A list of extra safe origin domains from which Server Actions can be invoked. Next.js compares the origin of a Server Action request
with the host domain, ensuring they match to prevent CSRF attacks. If not provided, only the same origin is allowed. next.config.js (js)/** @type {import('next').NextConfig} */
