Data returned from getInitialProps is serialized when server rendering. Ensure the returned object from
getInitialProps is a plain Object, and not using Date, Map or Set. For the initial page load, getInitialProps will run on the server only. getInitialProps will then also run on the client
when navigating to a different route with the next/link component or by using next/router. If getInitialProps is used in a custom _app.js, and the page being navigated to is using getServerSideProps, then
